                <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
                  <h1 class="mt-4">What would you do with the money you’d save if you didn’t have to pay your rent this month?</h1>
                  <p class="mt-4">Save it? Go on a holiday? Go on a shopping spree? Well, that could be a reality thanks to Flatmates.com.au's Live Rent Free competition. All you have to do is click the button to enter and be in the draw.
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                    Each month we’re giving one lucky member the equivalent of their suburb's average room rent for the month.* Be sure to enter each month for your chance to win a month rent free!</p>
                  <p class="mt-4 disclaimer">Not yet a Flatmates member? To enter this competition you need to have a verified flatmates.com.au account with a valid Australian mobile phone number and email address so that we can notify you if you have won.</p>
                </div>
