                      <li>Information on how to enter and the prize(s) form part of these<!-- -->
                        <a href="/live-rent-free/terms">Terms and Conditions</a>
                        . Participation in this promotion is deemed acceptance of these<!-- -->
                        <a href="/live-rent-free/terms">Terms and Conditions</a>
                        . All times are AEST/AEDST as the case requires.</li>
                      <li>The Promoter is flatmates.com.au Pty Ltd (ABN 78 168 397 582) of Level 17, 309 Kent Street, Sydney NSW 2000.</li>
                      <li>NSW Permit No. LTPS/17/15172. ACT Permit No. TP17/01169. SA Permit No. T17/1125</li>
                      <li>*The first valid entry drawn in each Monthly Draw will each win one month’s worth of rent (which will equate to 4.3 weeks) based on the average rent for a private room in their residing suburb (as confirmed at the time of winner notification). The amount awarded will be based on the www.flatmates.com.au<!-- -->
                        <a href="/value-my-room">Value My Room</a>
                        calculator and is up to the maximum value of $2,000. If there is no average rent for the residing suburb in the<!-- -->
                        <a href="/value-my-room">Value My Room</a>
                        calculator then the state average for the residing suburb will be used. For example, if the winner resides in Chippendale, NSW the average private room rent is $342 (as per the<!-- -->
                        <a href="/value-my-room">Value My Room</a>
                        Calculator as at 20/06/2017) multiplied by 4.3 weeks equates to $1,482.</li>
                    </ol>
                  </div>
